author: Matthew Boyle
title: Rep. Vern Buchanan Holds Off Thousands of Leftists Who Storm His Town Hall: ‘The Bottom Line Is’ Donald Trump ‘Won the Election’
text: Hard left-wing professional activists stormed a town hall held by Rep. Vern Buchanan (R-FL) here on Saturday morning, but the successful businessman-turned-congressman held his own and breezed through a rowdy capacity crowd’s efforts to disrupt President Donald Trump’s agenda.
